object.script:
BL = 0 PD = 0 P = 0 line = screen.drawLine cos = math.cos sin = math.sin rad = math.rad COL = screen.setColor WM = property.getBool("whisky marker") BG = property.getBool("background") LiD = math.ceil(property.getNumber("line degree")) function onTick() P = input.getNumber(1)*360 R = input.getNumber(2)*360 V = input.getNumber(3)
R2 = R-90 R3 = R+90 if V < 0 then P = P*-1 R = R R2 = R2*-1 else P = P*-1 R = R*-1 R2 = R2 end RD = rad(R) RD2 = rad(R2) LD = 25 SLD = 17 RC = cos(RD) RS = sin(RD) RC2 = cos(RD2) RC3 = cos(rad(R3)) RS2 = sin(RD2) PRS = P*RS2 PRC = P*RC2 MCP = math.ceil(P) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() w2 = w/2 h2 = h/2 if BG then COL(0,0,0) screen.drawRectF(0,0,w,h) end COL(0,255,255,255) if WM then line(w2,h2,w2-4,h2+3) line(w2-4,h2+3,w2-8,h2) line(w2-8,h2,w2-26,h2) line(w2,h2,w2+4,h2+3) line(w2+4,h2+3,w2+8,h2) line(w2+8,h2,w2+26,h2) end COL(255,0,0,200) line(w2-PRC+5*RC,h2-PRS-5*RS,w2-PRC+LD*RC,h2-PRS-LD*RS) line(w2-PRC-LD*RC,h2-PRS+LD*RS,w2-PRC-5*RC,h2-PRS+5*RS)
for PD = -LiD,-90,-LiD do if PD+MCP < 25 and PD+P > -25 then COL(0,255,0,250) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-7*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+7*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+7*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-7*RS) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC-3*RC2,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS-3*RS2) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC-3*RC2,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS-3*RS2) screen.drawText((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-4*RC,(h2-3-PD*RS2)-PRS,math.abs(PD)) end end for PD = LiD,90,LiD do if PD+MCP < 25 and PD+P > -25 then for BL = 7, SLD-1, 4 do SBL = BL+2 COL(0,255,0,250) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-BL*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+BL*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SBL*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SBL*RS) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SBL*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SBL*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+BL*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-BL*RS) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC+3*RC2,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS+3*RS2) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC+3*RC2,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS+3*RS2) screen.drawText((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-4*RC,(h2-3-PD*RS2)-PRS,PD) end end end
end

function onTick() batin = input.getNumber(1) xof = property.getNumber("x offset") yof = property.getNumber("y offset") battp = batin * 100 end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawClear() screen.setColor(255,255,255) w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.drawLine(7+xof,10+yof,7+xof,28+yof) screen.drawLine(24+xof,10+yof,24+xof,28+yof) screen.drawLine(7+xof,28+yof,25+xof,28+yof) screen.drawLine(8+xof,10+yof,12+xof,10+yof) screen.drawLine(20+xof,10+yof,25+xof,10+yof) screen.drawLine(12+xof,10+yof,12+xof,8+yof) screen.drawLine(19+xof,10+yof,19+xof,8+yof) screen.drawLine(12+xof,8+yof,20+xof,8+yof)
if battp < 10 then screen.setColor(255,17,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,25+yof,13,1) else if battp < 30 then screen.setColor(255,17,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,25+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,111,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,22+yof,13,1) else if battp < 50 then screen.setColor(255,17,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,25+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,111,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,22+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,238,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,19+yof,13,1) else if battp < 70 then screen.setColor(255,17,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,25+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,111,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,22+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,238,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,19+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(0,200,255) screen.drawRect(9+xof,16+yof,13,1) else if battp < 90 then screen.setColor(255,17,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,25+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,111,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,22+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,238,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,19+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(0,200,255) screen.drawRect(9+xof,16+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(34, 255, 0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,13+yof,13,1) else screen.setColor(255,17,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,25+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,111,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,22+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(255,238,0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,19+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(0,200,255) screen.drawRect(9+xof,16+yof,13,1) screen.setColor(34, 255, 0) screen.drawRect(9+xof,13+yof,13,1) end end end end end end

object.script:
function onTick() --Bank = input.getNumber(11) * 2 * math.pi --Pitch = input.getNumber(12) * 2 * math.pi ho = property.getNumber("Eyepoint_offset") P = input.getNumber(12) * 360 B0 = input.getNumber(11) pi = math.pi pi2 = math.pi * 2 B = (math.asin((math.sin(B0*pi2))/(math.sin((90-P)*(pi/180)))))*(180/pi) Up = input.getNumber(13)
if Up < 0 then B = 180-B end --(asin((sin(x*pi2))/(sin((90-y)*(pi/180)))))*(180/pi) BI = ((B + 180) % 360) - 180 output.setNumber(23, BI) output.setNumber(24, P) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() C = w/2 M = h/2 BR = math.rad(B) SB = math.sin(BR) *1.2 CB = math.cos(BR) *1.2 IC = C + (P*SB) * h/180 IM = M + (P*CB) * h/180 --L = (w+h)*2
screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawClear() screen.drawRectF(-2, -2, w+4, h+4)
--screen.setColor(32, 64, 96, 200) --screen.drawTriangleF(-CB*L+IC, SB*L+IM-ho, CB*L+IC, -SB*L+IM-ho, -SB*L+IC, -CB*L+IM-ho)
--screen.setColor(32, 16, 0, 200) --screen.drawTriangleF(-CB*L+IC, SB*L+IM-ho, CB*L+IC, -SB*L+IM-ho, SB*L+IC, CB*L+IM-ho)
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, 255) Xline(-90, 10, 2*w/32) Xline(90, 10, 2*w/32)
subline(0, 0, 10*w/32, 3*w/32, 192)
subline(-15*h/180*SB, -15*h/180*CB, 3*h/32, 1*h/32, 160) subline(-30*h/180*SB, -30*h/180*CB, 4*h/32, 1*h/32, 160) subline(-45*h/180*SB, -45*h/180*CB, 5*h/32, 1*h/32, 160) subline(-60*h/180*SB, -60*h/180*CB, 6*h/32, 1*h/32, 160) subline(-75*h/180*SB, -75*h/180*CB, 7*h/32, 1*h/32, 160)
subline(15*h/180*SB, 15*h/180*CB, 3*h/32, 1*h/32, 48) subline(30*h/180*SB, 30*h/180*CB, 4*h/32, 1*h/32, 48) subline(45*h/180*SB, 45*h/180*CB, 5*h/32, 1*h/32, 48) subline(60*h/180*SB, 60*h/180*CB, 6*h/32, 1*h/32, 48) subline(75*h/180*SB, 75*h/180*CB, 7*h/32, 1*h/32, 48)
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 255) --skypointer screen.drawTriangleF(w/2 - 6*h/32*SB, h/2-ho - 6*h/32*CB, w/2 - 5*h/32*math.sin(BR-1/6), h/2-ho - 5*h/32*math.cos(BR-1/6), w/2 - 5*h/32*math.sin(BR+1/6), h/2-ho - 5*h/32*math.cos(BR+1/6))
end
function subline(X, Y, len, SP, alpha) screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, alpha) screen.drawLine((-len*CB)+X+IC, (len*SB)+Y+IM-ho, (len*CB)+X+IC, (-len*SB)+Y+IM-ho) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawLine((-SP*CB)+X+IC, (SP*SB)+Y+IM-ho, (SP*CB)+X+IC, (-SP*SB)+Y+IM-ho) end
function Xline(deg, degD, len) X1 = (deg - degD) * h/180 * SB Y1 = (deg - degD) * h/180 * CB X2 = (deg + degD) * h/180 * SB Y2 = (deg + degD) * h/180 * CB screen.drawLine((-len*CB)+X1+IC, (len*SB)+Y1+IM-ho, (len*CB)+X2+IC, (-len*SB)+Y2+IM-ho) screen.drawLine((-len*CB)+X2+IC, (len*SB)+Y2+IM-ho, (len*CB)+X1+IC, (-len*SB)+Y1+IM-ho) end

FD = false CH1 = true CH2 = false CH3 = false CH4 = false FDCH = 1
Mode = "N" function onTick() ho = property.getNumber("Eyepoint_offset") AltU = property.getNumber("AltimeterUnit") SpdU = property.getNumber("SpeedUnit")
TW = input.getNumber(1) TH = input.getNumber(2) inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4)
SpdBug = Round(adjNum(input.getNumber(7), 1, 0), 1)
if AltU == 1 then AltBug = Round(adjNum(input.getNumber(8), 1, 0), 1) else AltBug = Round(adjNum(input.getNumber(8), 2, 0), 1) end
HdgBug = Round(input.getNumber(9), 3)
B = input.getNumber(23) P = input.getNumber(24)
isPressed = input.getBool(1) ResetBTN = isPressed and isInRect(inputX, inputY, -1, TH-8, 7, 8)
if isPressed and isInRect(inputX, inputY, 6, TH-8, 7, 8) then Mode = "N" FD = false
elseif isPressed and isInRect(inputX, inputY, 13, TH-8, 7, 8) then Mode = "F" FD = true
end
if isPressed and isInRect(inputX, inputY, TW-28, TH-8, 7, 8) then CH1 = true CH2 = false CH3 = false CH4 = false FDCH = 1
elseif isPressed and isInRect(inputX, inputY, TW-21, TH-8, 7, 8) then CH1 = false CH2 = true CH3 = false CH4 = false FDCH = 2
elseif isPressed and isInRect(inputX, inputY, TW-14, TH-8, 7, 8) then CH1 = false CH2 = false CH3 = true CH4 = false FDCH = 3
elseif isPressed and isInRect(inputX, inputY, TW-7, TH-8, 7, 8) then CH1 = false CH2 = false CH3 = false CH4 = true FDCH = 4
end
C = TW/2 M = TH/2 BR = math.rad(B) CB = math.cos(BR) IM = M + (P*CB) output.setBool(32, ResetBTN) output.setBool(31, FD) output.setNumber(31, FDCH) --output.setBool(30, CH2) --output.setBool(29, CH3) --output.setBool(28, CH4)
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(0,255,0,200) if ResetBTN then screen.drawRectF(0, TH-7, 6, 7) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawText(1, TH-6, "R") else screen.drawText(1, TH-6, "R") end
screen.setColor(0,255,0,200) if Mode == "N" then screen.drawRectF(7, TH-7, 6, 7) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawText(8, TH-6, "N") else screen.drawText(8, TH-6, "N") end
screen.setColor(0,255,0,200) if Mode == "F" then screen.drawRectF(14, TH-7, 6, 7) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawText(15, TH-6, "F") else screen.drawText(15, TH-6, "F") end
screen.setColor(0,255,0,200) if CH1 then screen.drawRectF(w-27, TH-7, 6, 7) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawText(w-26, TH-6, "1") else screen.drawText(w-26, TH-6, "1") end
screen.setColor(0,255,0,200) if CH2 then screen.drawRectF(w-20, TH-7, 6, 7) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawText(w-19, TH-6, "2") else screen.drawText(w-19, TH-6, "2") end
screen.setColor(0,255,0,200) if CH3 then screen.drawRectF(w-13, TH-7, 6, 7) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawText(w-12, TH-6, "3") else screen.drawText(w-12, TH-6, "3") end
screen.setColor(0,255,0,200) if CH4 then screen.drawRectF(w-6, TH-7, 6, 7) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawText(w-5, TH-6, "4") else screen.drawText(w-5, TH-6, "4") end
end
function Round(num, lead) return string.format("%0"..lead..".0f", num) end
function adjNum(num, zero, offset) return math.floor(num/(10^zero)+0.5)*(10^zero) + offset end
function rMarkC(deg, length, center) if deg > 0 then offset_w = -1 else offset_w = 0 end screen.drawLine(w/2 + offset_w - center * math.sin(deg), h/2 -ho -1 - center * math.cos(deg), w/2 + offset_w - (center + length) * math.sin(deg), h/2 -ho -1 - (center + length) * math.cos(deg)) end
function isInRect(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end

sc = screen scdRF = screen.drawRectF scdTB = screen.drawTextBox scC = screen.setColor Mt = math iN = input.getNumber TA = 15 DSPD = {} AVSI = {} TC = {} LAST_ALT = 0 LAST_SPD = 0 LAST_T = 0 for i = 1, 60, 1 do DSPD[i] = 0 AVSI[i] = 0 TC[i] = 0 end
function onTick() AltU = property.getNumber("AltimeterUnit") SpdU = property.getNumber("SpeedUnit")
ALT = iN(1) * AltU SPD = iN(3) T = -iN(5) CP = iN(6) HD = Round(((-CP*360)%360), 3) P = Mt.min(Mt.max(iN(7), -0.125), 0.125)*8 SpdBug = adjNum(iN(8), 1, 0) if AltU == 1 then AltBug = adjNum(iN(9), 1, 0) else AltBug = adjNum(iN(9), 2, 0) end for i = TA, 2, -1 do DSPD[i] = DSPD[i-1] AVSI[i] = AVSI[i-1] TC[i] = TC[i-1] end DSPD[1] = SPD - LAST_SPD AVSI[1] = ALT - LAST_ALT if Mt.abs(T - LAST_T) < 0.5 then TC[1] = T - LAST_T end
VSI = 0 SPDT = 0 TN = 0 for i = 1, TA, 1 do VSI = VSI+AVSI[i] SPDT = SPDT+DSPD[i] TN = TN + TC[i] end TN = TN /TA * 3600 if AltU == 1 then --m/s VSI = VSI * 60 / TA else --fpm VSI = VSI * 3600 / TA / 100 end LAST_ALT = ALT LAST_SPD = SPD SPD = SPD * SpdU end
function onDraw() w = sc.getWidth() h = sc.getHeight() if w >= 96 and h >= 96 then --back mask scC(0, 0, 0) scdRF(0, 0, 28, h) scdRF(w-28, 0, 28, h) scdRF(0, 0, w, 6)
-- tape+mask for i = 1, 3, 1 do ajn = adjNum(SPD, 1, 10*i) if ajn == SpdBug then paint(-1, h/2-5-((ajn-SPD)/10*7), 27, 7) else scC(0, 255, 0, 200) end scdTB(-1, h/2-4-((ajn-SPD)/10*7), 26, 7, Round(ajn,1), 1, -1)
ajn = adjNum(SPD, 1, 10-10*i) if ajn >= 0 then if ajn == SpdBug then paint(-1, h/2-5-((ajn-SPD)/10*7), 27, 7) else scC(0, 255, 0, 200) end scdTB(-1, h/2-4-((ajn-SPD)/10*7), 26, 7, Round(ajn,1), 1, -1) end
ajn = adjNum(ALT, 2, 100*i) if ajn == AltBug then paint(w-26, h/2-5-((ajn-ALT)/100*7), 27, 7) else scC(0, 255, 0, 200) end scdTB(w-27, h/2-4-((ajn-ALT)/100*7), 26, 7, Round(ajn,1), 1, -1)
ajn = adjNum(ALT, 2, 100-100*i) if ajn >= 0 then if ajn == AltBug then paint(w-26, h/2-5-((ajn-ALT)/100*7), 27, 7) else scC(0, 255, 0, 200) end scdTB(w-27, h/2-4-((ajn-ALT)/100*7), 26, 7, Round(ajn,1), 1, -1) end end
for i = 1, 6, 1 do scC(0, 0, 0, i*32+63) scdRF(0, h/2-7-i*2, 28, 2) scdRF(0, h/2+2+i*2, 28, 2) scdRF(w-28, h/2-7-i*2, 28, 2) scdRF(w-28, h/2+2+i*2, 28, 2) end
scdRF(0, h/2-31, 28, 12) scdRF(0, h/2+14, 28, 12) scdRF(w-28, h/2-31, 28, 12) scdRF(w-28, h/2+14, 28, 12)
-- Main Mask scC(0, 0, 0) scdRF(-2, h/2-7, 30, 11) scdRF(w-28, h/2-7, 30, 11)
-- Speed Trend SPDTB = Mt.min(Mt.max(SPDT, -10), 10)/10*12 scC(0, 255, 0, 100)
if SPDT > 0 then scdRF(0, h/2-6, 5, -SPDTB) elseif SPDT < 0 then scdRF(0, h/2+3, 5, -SPDTB) end
scC(0, 255, 0, 200) -- AirSpeed sc.drawRect(-2, h/2-6, 28, 8) scdTB(-1, h/2-4, 26, 7, Round(SPD,1), 1, -1)
